  - **dst**: `Evision.Mat`.

    Second input 3D point set.

  ##### Keyword Arguments
  - **force_rotation**: `bool`.

    If true, the returned rotation will never be a reflection.
    This might be unwanted, e.g. when optimizing a transform between a right- and a
    left-handed coordinate system.

  ##### Return
